Description: Naurto learns more secrets from his past and moves closer to discovering the identity of his nemesis, Pain.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 47
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 30
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 1
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 9
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 2
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Alice’s exploration of this strange wonderland continues. In this world, everyone has clocks for hearts. Because they can be easily repaired, life is valued less.
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF HEARTS, VOL. 2
Author: Quinrose and Soumei Hoshino

Description:
Alice wanders into a very different part of Wonderland in this interpretation of the classic tale. 

In this new area of the fantasy land, every man is in love with Alice... and firearms.
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF HEARTS: THE CLOCKMAKER'S STORY
Author: Quinrose and Soumei Hoshino

Description: Fate Averruncus gives Negi a choice: fight him and save the world or flee and guarantee his student’s safety.
Title: NEGIMA! (MAGISTER NEGI MAGI), VOL. 25
Author: Ken Akamatsu

Description: Shouldn’t having wings be fun? That’s not the case for 14-year-old Maximum Ride and her friends who are hunted by a organization called "The School."
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE, VOL. 1
Author: James Patterson and NaRae Lee
Contributor: by James Patterson and NaRae Lee

Description: Kyoko tries to create a Christmas miracle. Can she cheer up Maria, who has a very good reason for enjoying the holiday season?
Title: SKIP BEAT!, VOL. 20
Author: Yoshiki Nakamura
